<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta name="author" content="Pacifique Murangwa  - {pacifiquem@github.com}">
        <meta name="discription" content="Website for secure filesharing">
        <meta name="keywords" content="filesharing, secure filesharing, p-FileSharing">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="3600">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
        <script src="script.js" defer></script>
        <title>FS.simplifier &nbsp; - &nbsp; Home</title>
    </head>
    <body onload="addEvents()">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="logo">
                    <h1>FS.simplifier</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="nav">
                    <nav>
                        <ul>
                            <li><a href="#">Instructions</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Features</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </nav>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="body">
                <div class="form">
                    <h1>Share Files with Password Protection</h1>
                    <form action="http://localhost:4220/file" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                        <div class="inputs">
                            <div class="input-label-div">
                                <label for="file-input">
                                    Upload File 
                                    <input type="file" id="file-input" name="uploadedFile" />
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="input-label-div password-div">
                                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Enter Password" id="pass-input">
                                <p style="display: none;" id="para-label">Password</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit">Share</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="discription">
                    <h1>File Sharing simplifier</h1>
                    <p>FS.simplifier allows you to share files and protect them with password.</p>
                    <p>You can easily share url generated after uploading a file whenever you want to send that file.</p>
                    <p>After sharing the link, people who know the password that protects that file can download it.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>pacifiquem Â© All rights Reserved</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>